  "title": "Roadshow Promoter!!!",
  "description": "<p>🌟Roadshow Promoter- Join the team now!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for energetic, confident, and customer-friendly individuals to join our team as Roadshow Promoters. In this role, you will promote products or services at roadshow booths, engage with the public, and help drive sales or sign-ups.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Approach and engage with customers at roadshow locations</li><li>Promote and explain products, services, or promotions</li><li>Demonstrate products when required</li><li>Encourage sales, sign-ups, or participation</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Outgoing, friendly, and comfortable interacting with crowds</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and able to work flexible hours</li></ul>",
